The '''Puerto Rico Special Weapons and Tactics''' is the [[SWAT]] division of the [[Puerto Rico Police]] that intervenes in hostage rescue situations, operations against snipers, search and arrest dangerous fugitives, and support of other police units.<ref name="swat-at-pr-police-website" /> The division was formed in 1979 as a reaction to the [[Munich massacre]] since [[Puerto Rico]] was close to hold the [[1979 Pan American Games]].<ref name="swat-history-by-pr-police" />

